rungs.comment: Use the Auto switch to enable and put the robot into run mode
Short delay before restarting the robot

Mechatronics Program
87-MS5
Assembly
Allen-Bradley CompactLogix PLC
1769-L16ER-BB1B CPU

Spool Empty Faults:  If an attempt to start the cycle is made, and the spool type needed by the valve body to be loaded is not present, a fault for the spool type is generated.  This fault can only be reset if the spool type that generated the fault is present.
